Sentencas: The electrochemical performance of Ca3Co4O9+delta (CCO) oxygen electrode with La0.6Sr0.4FeO3-delta (LSF) interlayer in YSZ-based reversible solid oxide cells (RSOCs) was investigated in present work.
Titulo: Study of Ca3Co4O9+δ oxygen electrode with La0.6Sr0.4FeO3-δ interlayer in YSZ-based reversible solid oxide cells

Sentencas: Results proved that CCO oxygen electrode with LSF interlayer had a superior stability under alternating anodic and cathodic polarization.
Titulo: Study of Ca3Co4O9+δ oxygen electrode with La0.6Sr0.4FeO3-δ interlayer in YSZ-based reversible solid oxide cells

Sentencas: Both the polarization resistance and overpotential of the CCO electrode with LSF interlayer were significantly reduced compared to that with Ce0.9Gd0.1O1.95 (GDC) interlayer, which confirmed the improvement of the redox reactivity of the oxygen electrode.
Titulo: Study of Ca3Co4O9+δ oxygen electrode with La0.6Sr0.4FeO3-δ interlayer in YSZ-based reversible solid oxide cells

Sentencas: The maximum power density of Ni-YSZ/YSZ/LSF/CCO fuel cell was 1276 mW cm(-2) at 800 degrees C. An electrolysis current density of 1695 mA cm(-2) was achieved at 1.5 V and 50% H2O.
Titulo: Study of Ca3Co4O9+δ oxygen electrode with La0.6Sr0.4FeO3-δ interlayer in YSZ-based reversible solid oxide cells

Sentencas: The hydrogen production rate of the electrolysis cell improved by 2 times than that with the GDC interlayer.
Titulo: Study of Ca3Co4O9+δ oxygen electrode with La0.6Sr0.4FeO3-δ interlayer in YSZ-based reversible solid oxide cells

Sentencas: Results made clear reliability of LSF as an interlayer in YSZ-based RSOCs.(c) 2023
